    "Many researchers related to the RIPS have found the effectiveness and robustness of controllers using the NN with fuzzy such as radial basis neuro-fuzzy [9] and fuzzy-based multi-layer feed-forward neural networks [10].DL has made a vast contribution to solving the complexity of nonlinearity and instability of the systems.",
